Sport champions of 2º Turno
3º Turno
Náutico winners of 1st Phase
Santa Cruz winners of 2nd Phase
Final: Santa Cruz 1-1 Náutico
Santa Cruz champions of 3º Turno due to have better campaign.
FINAL
16/Aug  Sport 1-1 Santa Cruz
Santa Cruz champions of 1987 due to had won both 1º and 3º Turnos against
only the 2º Turno won by Sport.
